APPLICATIONS_ON_APARAJIT:
	This folder contains Matrix Multiplication and FFT implemented and tested for APARAJIT on VCU118 board.

KCU105_bitfiles:
	contains KCU105 bitfiles for SBC

SBC:
	Files for the SBC (Processor + DRAM + Ethernet) design on the VCU118 and KCU105

VCU118_Aparajit:
	Files for Aparajit SBC design on VCU118

VCU118_Aparajit_bitfiles:
	contains VCU118 bitfiles for APARAJIT SBC

VCU118_SBC_bitfiles:
	contains VCU118 bitfiles for SBC

BUILD:
	Implementation of NIC and NIC glue logic. (from AmanD15/AI_NIC_DEMO)

Networking:
	Contains the NIC implementation. (from AmanD15/AI_NIC_DEMO)
